Libraries:
* Three.Js => 
    React-three-fiber: react renderer for three.js
    React-three-drei: usefull addons for fiber

* Maath: usefull math helpers meant to with used for three.js 
* Valtio: a new package that allows us to easly use react state
* framer-motion: for cool animations
* TailwindCSS, postCSS, autoprefixer: for easly CSS integration

